{"tid":1252371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"齊來提防扮獨立真建制議員","createTime":"2019-06-23T03:42:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T09:52:40.000Z","uid":159342,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8e9933b42029f8bd1224021eb58fb5077485c459","tid":1252371,"uid":159342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T03:42:34.000Z","msg":"年尾就區議會選舉，相比起旗幟鮮明既建制派明箭，果堆扮獨立真建制既候選人既暗箭絕對難防。<br />\n<br />\n經歷過69，616大遊行，612事件，建制內鬥割蓆，黎緊選舉一定會有好多聲稱獨立人士，抽住反對逃犯條例修訂草案水既隱形建制派出選。<br />\n<br />\n其實係連登有冇可能集思廣益，設立一個平台幫大家分辨果堆聲稱獨立人士，但唔知佢咩來歷既人，睇下佢係真獨立，定係隱形建制"},{"pid":"a552bd35cec11074a47531884189160af944c18c","tid":1252371,"uid":159342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T04:57:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eefcebb0ac350821d9f2db0289c218b3824aaf9b","tid":1252371,"uid":263448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T04:58:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f1bedd46219c47b0015c985c943ba96f7614ce5","tid":1252371,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T04:59:26.000Z","msg":"中間超人好易分<br />\n<br />\n唔講政治談民生"},{"pid":"70e480d7c4eec6431e8f050757081ecf95a2ed2e","tid":1252371,"uid":31296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T05:00:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"30129e97865267e7fb2b7c02d3254283360b2d35","tid":1252371,"uid":159342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f1bedd46219c47b0015c985c943ba96f7614ce5","tid":1252371,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T04:59:26.000Z","msg":"中間超人好易分<br />\n<br />\n唔講政治談民生"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T05:09:11.000Z","msg":"主要想幫首投族分辨果堆偽獨立議員，如果大家一齊俾料幫大家分辨（公海有幾個區議會post都做緊類似既野）就好"},{"pid":"ae4c51d602136c79e7df69c7df2f6211118ddc0c","tid":1252371,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30129e97865267e7fb2b7c02d3254283360b2d35","tid":1252371,"uid":159342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{